title: Spacious & Affordable 1 Bedroom Apartment Home Available!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Welcome to Elm Creek Apartments in Champlin, MN.', 'Elm Creek is more than just a place to live.', 'Our spacious one, two and three bedroom floor plans offer plenty of space to make your home comfortable for you and your family.', 'Our community has all the perks you’ve been looking for!', 'You’ll enjoy our sand volleyball court, basketball court, and community center.', 'Call our wonderful on-site management staff today to schedule a tour of your new home!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Maple Cabinetry & Countertops', '- Huge Open Lawn Space', '- Individually Controlled Air-Conditioning System', '- Ceiling Fan(s) & Microwave (select homes)', '- Professional On-Site Management', '- Ample Counter Top & Cabinet Space', '- Ample Off-Street Open Parking', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'ElmCreek participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-2:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Elmcreek Apartments', '11719 Champlin Drive', 'Champlin, MN, 55316', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '4VZ1q0aqWfF']
